Directory & Domain Server

Provides native compatibility with Microsoft Active Directory®, allowing you to join Microsoft® clients to a domain and manage them easily.
Mail Server

Provides a mail server together with webmail and synchronization to mobile devices via ActiveSync.
Gateway

Provides reliable and secure Internet access while helping to manage traffic and speed navigation.
Infrastructure Server

Unifies and allows to easily manage all the basic network infrastructure.

